body:
Here the list of the characters, for those who dont know who is in this doujin, in order: (through investigating):
-Sage (Dragon Quest III)
-Coltia (Monster Rancher 2)
-Witch and Draco (Puyo Puyo)
-Lolo (Klonoa 2)
-White Mage "Shirma" (Chocobo´s Mysterious Dungeon)
-Mikachu (Tamagotchi)
-Casi (Ape Escape)
-That female warrior from (RPG Maker 3 for PS1)
-Call (Mighty No.9)
-Yae (Ganbare Goemon)
-Pino (Wonder Project J)
-Konami Girl (Wai Wai World)
-Ki and Ishtar (Tower of Druaga)
-Windy,Thiana and Neris (Panel de Pon)
-Lieza (Arc the Lad II)
-Dont know their names but im pretty sure they are from (Dokapon Gaiden for SNES)
-World (Magical Drop)
-Fairy Queen (Kirby The Crystal Shards)
-Sue Sakamoto (Cave Story)
One of these things is not like the others. . .
